<2.0.0>
- Complete refactor of database management system with migration support
- Added console commands for database seeding and verification (bcc-stashes:seed, bcc-stashes:verify)
- Added PickupEmptyOnly restriction for chest types in configuration
- Fixed critical entity handling bugs in resource cleanup
- Enhanced client-side chest interaction with proper state management
- Improved inventory registration for dynamically created chests
- Updated comprehensive error handling and debugging system
- Updated all language files with complete translations (EN, DE, FR, RO)
- Changed job system to use JobRestrictions with individual job grades instead of JobName/JobGrades arrays

